{"tid":783504,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"變形金剛界最近好似幾亂","createTime":"2018-08-17T14:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T18:12:12.000Z","uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62c30543c8772da0b51d103cd4856968eb3ac6b1","tid":783504,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"我不是玩具人<br />\n我是收藏玩具的創作者<br />\n玩具只是一個媒介<br />\n因為我也是一位父親<br />\n我希望能分享我認為正確的價值觀<br />\n畢竟還是有未成年的觀眾<br />\n但世風日下<br />\n倡導版權觀念、不貪小便宜<br />\n也淪為被攻擊的點<br />\n同業惡意的抹黑、hater的人身攻擊<br />\n甚至扯到我的家人<br />\n我知道這些人因為一事無成只剩下鍵盤<br />\n面對攻擊我從來也不會退縮<br />\n但畢竟我只是一個愛分享創作的普通人<br />\n面對這些我有些灰心<br />\n這只是一個興趣<br />\n我也沒利用自己的知名度賺粉絲的錢<br />\n真的是吃力不討好<br />\n不做影片，我的經濟完全不受影響<br />\n在創作這條路上<br />\n我需要各位的鼓勵<br />\n讓我有堅持下去的理由<br />\n還是感謝各位一路的支持<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/224707_97dc5aad2a889d5e0151bd5d8b966927.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F224707_97dc5aad2a889d5e0151bd5d8b966927.png&h=4b1709b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"923dd76051a87222cf718bc237a9aa769fc1d333","tid":783504,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"變形金剛界又真係幾亂<br />\n又狂派又博派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cededd0e02422f4a61129ec776eba3e09688d3","tid":783504,"uid":31651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"923dd76051a87222cf718bc237a9aa769fc1d333","tid":783504,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"變形金剛界又真係幾亂<br />\n又狂派又博派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}